# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  We'll Share — Angular Frontend  |  .gitignore
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Compiled & Build Output ───────────────────────────
/dist
/tmp
/out-tsc
/bazel-out

# ── Angular CLI Cache ─────────────────────────────────
/.angular
.angular/

# ── Dependencies (never commit these) ────────────────
/node_modules
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log
yarn.lock

# ── Environment & Secret Files ────────────────────────
# These contain API keys, backend URLs, secrets — DO NOT commit
.env
.env.*
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production
*.local

# Angular environment files (use environment.example.ts as template)
src/environments/environment.prod.ts
src/environments/environment.development.ts

# ── IDE & Editor Files ────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.history/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
*.sublime-workspace
.project
.classpath
.c9/
*.launch
.settings/

# ── Testing & Coverage ────────────────────────────────
/coverage
.nyc_output

# ── OS Generated Files ────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/
/connect.lock
/libpeerconnection.log
testem.log

# ── Misc ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.sass-cache/
/typings
*.zip
*.tar.gz
